dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2022 and includes the layers 'Jefferson_General_2022' and 'Jefferson_Shoreland_2018' and the table 'JEFFERSON_ZONING_CODES_2022.' While the general zoning data is current to 2022, the shoreland zoning data is dated 2018. [General: This file contains the polygons for all parcels in Jefferson County and the data related to the zoning designation for all tax parcels.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
